column16: Adam Wainwright doubles (2) on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Frank Catalanotto.
Brendan Ryan grounds out, shortstop Jose Reyes to first baseman Fernando Tatis.
David Freese lines out to shortstop Jose Reyes.
Yadier Molina grounds out, second baseman Alex Cora to first baseman Fernando Tatis.
Colby Rasmus grounds out to first baseman Fernando Tatis.    Matt Holliday to 3rd.
Matt Holliday doubles (3) on a line drive to right fielder Jeff Francoeur.
Albert Pujols flies out to center fielder Angel Pagan.

Adam Wainwright lines out to center fielder Angel Pagan.
Brendan Ryan singles on a ground ball to center fielder Angel Pagan.
